graph LR
    KServe[KServe Operator<br/>v6a07b522b]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KServe -->|requires| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.24+<br/>Container Orchestration]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional but Recommended)
    KServe -->|serverless autoscaling| Knative[Knative Serving 1.8+<br/>Scale-to-Zero]
    KServe -->|traffic mgmt + mTLS| Istio[Istio 1.16+<br/>Service Mesh]
    KServe -->|webhook TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager 1.9+<br/>Certificate Management]
    KServe -.->|raw deployment mode| HPA[Kubernetes HPA<br/>CPU/Memory Autoscaling]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    KServe -->|ingress + routing| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh Istio<br/>VirtualService/Gateway]
    KServe -->|inference authz| Authorino[Authorino<br/>JWT Validation]
    KServe -->|model metadata| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Versioning/Lineage]
    KServe -.->|managed by| DataScienceCluster[DataScienceCluster<br/>Component Lifecycle]

    %% Integration Points (Consume KServe)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>UI Management] -->|manages| KServe
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Auto-Deploy] -->|deploys models| KServe

    %% External Services (Storage)
    KServe -->|model artifacts| S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>AWS S3/MinIO/Ceph]
    KServe -->|model artifacts| GCS[Google Cloud Storage<br/>GCP]
    KServe -->|model artifacts| Azure[Azure Blob Storage<br/>Azure Cloud]

    %% Kubernetes API
    KServe -->|CRD management| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    Kubernetes -.->|provides| K8sAPI

    %% Runtime Dependencies
    subgraph "Serving Runtimes"
